<p>
    <br> <span> What is critical thinking? </span>
    <br>

    <br>Critical thinking is thinking and making good judgments based on reliable information to yield the best result.
    <br>
    <br><span> Why is it a vital part of geopgrahic inquiry?</span>
    <br>
    <br>Critical thinking is an important part of the geographic inquiry. Critical thinking in a group can be vital because calmly and rationally solving a problem can make everyone feel included.
